flowchart TD
    INIT["`1. Choose k Initialise k centroids (random or k-means++)`"]
    INIT --> ASSIGN["`2. Assign Each point → nearest centroid (Euclidean distance)`"]
    ASSIGN --> UPDATE["3. Update Recompute centroid as cluster mean"]
    UPDATE --> CHECK{Centroids changed?}
    CHECK -->|Yes| ASSIGN
    CHECK -->|No| DONE["Converged Return labels + centroids"]

    subgraph LIMITS["Common failure modes"]
        F1["`Sensitive to initialisation Fix: k-means++ (sklearn default)`"]
        F2["Assumes spherical clusters Fix: DBSCAN or GMM for irregular shapes"]
        F3["Must specify k Fix: Elbow / silhouette to choose k"]
        F4["Sensitive to scale Fix: StandardScaler before fitting"]
    end
